<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/jan/31/">&#x27a0;</a> January 31, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="blogzilla_drmagogo" >

        
        <a name="002249"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://dooooooom.blogspot.com/2006/01/drm-go-go.html">Blogzilla: DRM-a-go-go</a></h4>

        

        <p>&#8216;DRM-protected files exclusively released through iTunes &#8230; appear in unprotected form on P2P networks 180 seconds later&#8217;.  Well, that makes screwing your honest customers worthwhile.</p>

